{"tid":1639298,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"#我們的餘生將在抗爭中度過 [序]","createTime":"2019-10-08T14:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T15:38:32.000Z","uid":20035,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0b3e6dbf183d118198636806bf889743688eef98","tid":1639298,"uid":20035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:46:50.000Z","msg":"#我們的餘生將在抗爭中度過<br />\n<br />\n香港人從來都沒有選擇，直到現在。<br />\n<br />\n自從在矇昧裡覺醒，我們只能直面真相&mdash;&mdash;無論它何其殘酷，教人顫慄。<br />\n<br />\n歷史選中了我們。這一場仗關乎良知，關乎自由正義，更關乎我們與下一代將來的家園。哪怕要用多少汗水、時間，甚至鮮血來灌溉，我們也願以勇氣和信念回應時代，打破宿命，不當逃兵。<br />\n<br />\n縱使餘生將在抗爭中度過，我們仍然會團結一致，堅守陣地直到黎明。要達致五大訴求，我們相信有以下三大路線：<br />\n<br />\n1. 非暴力抗爭，例如：罷工、罷稅、平行政府，用不合作手段癱瘓社會以瓦解政權；<br />\n<br />\n2. 集體武力反抗，以正義之戰來推翻暴政；<br />\n<br />\n3. 爭取國際支援，包括外國勢力以軟硬方式介入。軟性指經濟制裁、外交干涉，硬性則指提供武器、出動軍隊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重光香港，現在開始：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.me/libco.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Flibco.hk&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VnJTAtm2oKGHsrawk8oVPbs%3D&h=82065e3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.me/libco.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://instagram.com/libco.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Flibco.hk&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VnJTAtm2oKGHsrawk8oVPbs%3D&h=7fe7045d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/libco.hk</a>"},{"pid":"7ae73e780cc5f5c1918c9b2bf0828c211ea11505","tid":1639298,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:47:07.000Z","msg":"【極重要】唔好再打跨區喇！係打就開花！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639294</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ed3c81e629532a5fe4aa3b0585a13ac09e0071bc","tid":1639298,"uid":20035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x7a1RDT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx7a1RDT.jpg&h=4362bf25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1733e34